reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 21, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars It's small, and it works
reviews.reviewText: For the price, you can't beat it. Worked out of the box for the most part - really nothing to complain about. It's a motherboard that lets the computer run

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 5, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I got it to boot up using Linux, however when I try to install it cannot do so. I tried using sata SSD 4tb crucial and a micron nvme m.2 drive and neither works. I can't find the drivers or bios update and the manufacturer is unknown. I will need to return this

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on May 16, 2021
reviews.reviewText: Replaced my Dell Vostro 270 mobo with this one. Very happy with the results. My NVME is a Samsung 970 and speeds are at ~1300 x 1400, which makes me think it’s gen 3. I’m not convinced the network adapter is full gigabit, as download speeds seem slower than the stock mobo.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 18, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Ya e tenido problemas con este articulo incluso se me volvió a dañar pero no voy a seguir reclamando prefiero perder poco dinero que mi tiempo ... muchas gracias Amazon no es su culpa...

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on June 21, 2021
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars no Está nada mal por el precio
reviews.reviewText: Es relativamente estable para trabajos domésticos, lo malo es que no tiene especificaciones ni driver del fabricante

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 24, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 2.0 out of 5 stars Works but has one big issue
reviews.reviewText: Everything went well in Windows 11/10 installation. All drivers were downloaded from Microsoft during installation although it does not have the ability to go into sleep mode. No way to change that in the bios so it will never go into hibernate or sleep mode. It allows the ability to automatically turn off the monitor off but that's it. That is not acceptable.

reviews.reviewTitle: 1.0 out of 5 stars Did not work... total dud
reviews.reviewText: Installed and everything only to find out the board was a dead upon arrival. Junk. Do not buy it.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 24, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Tech support never got in touch re
reviews.reviewText: Just a few games mostly general workstation (thought the board had issues but tech support never got back to me turned out it was the psu i ordered for this board 8 pin cpu power) it is working fine now
